            .index-schedule-item__right
              h3 It Won't Make a Noise When it Breaks
              .index-schedule-item__right--text
                p Systems fail but the real failures are the ones from those we learn nothing. This talk is a tale of few such failures that went right under our noses and what we did to prevent those. The failures covered range from Heterogenous systems, unordered events, missing correlations and just human errors.
