              .index-schedule-item__right--text
                p Multi-core systems are around for quite some time now. But lot of applications are not written to take full advantage of the parallalizm it provides to the applications, improving the performance. This talk will cover multiple advantages multi-core systems provide and will also point out the challenges in multi-core programming. This will also cover real-life examples of multi-core programming.
